  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare postoperative immune function (e.g. NK cell activity)
      of fentanyl-based analgesic regimen versus local anesthetic wound infiltration-based
      anlagesic regimen after laparoscopic colorectal surgery
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
